@startuml UEORMS_State_11
top to bottom direction
hide empty description
title UEORMS State Transition - 11) Reports, Data Utilities, and Integration

[*] --> ReportRequestDraft
ReportRequestDraft --> ReportGenerated : generate report
ReportGenerated --> ReportSaved : save report
ReportSaved --> ReportExported : export report
ReportSaved --> ReportScheduled : schedule report
ReportExported --> DataImportPending : optional import
ReportScheduled --> DataImportPending : optional import
DataImportPending --> DataImported : import complete
DataImported --> DataExported : export operational data
DataExported --> SyncRequested : cross-module sync
SyncRequested --> SyncRunning : integration worker running
SyncRunning --> SyncSucceeded : sync success
SyncRunning --> SyncFailed : sync failure
SyncFailed --> SyncRequested : retry
SyncSucceeded --> IntegrationMonitored : monitor status/config
IntegrationMonitored --> [*]

@enduml
